      "description": "CFD-predicted normalized index of hemolysis (NIH) compared against published FDA generic centrifugal pump experimental measurements at 5 operating points. Mean relative error 8.3%; all predictions within experimental uncertainty bounds. RH < 1 criterion satisfied at all conditions."
    },
